import "./barstyle.css"
import Secrete from "../pages/secret.js"
export default function bar() {
    return(
        <>
        <Router>
            <Navbar />
            <Routes>
                <Route exact path="/" element={<Home />} />
                <Route path="/about" element={<About />} />
                <Route
                    path="/contact"
                    element={<Contact />}
                />
                <Route path="/blogs" element={<Blogs />} />
                <Route
                    path="/sign-up"
                    element={<SignUp />}
                />
            </Routes>
        </Router>
        </>
    )
}
